  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of the the FUSION™ Vascular
      Graft.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study is a prospective, single arm, multi-center study to evaluate the FUSION™ Vascular
      Graft patency at 30 days, 6 months, 1 year and post operative complications not associated
      with bypass patency.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
